text: Agdistis clara is a moth in the family Pterophoridae. It is known from Namibia, Botswana and South Africa.New Species and Records of Plume Moths of the Genus Agdistis Hübner, 1825 (Lepidoptera: Pterophoridae, Agdistinae) from Southern Africa ==References== Category:Agdistinae Category:Moths of Africa Category:Plume moths of Africa Category:Moths described in 1986
